   Chrysler Corp. rose ] to 24\. The company reported
second-quarter earnings of $1.46 a share, up from $1.45 in the like
period last year.
   Elsewhere among the blue chips, American Telephone &amp; Telegraph
gained ] to 40{; International Business Machines 1\ to 114|; Philip
Morris 2 to 157, and General Electric ] to 57~.
